
footer {
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  padding: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.footer-buttons button {
  margin: 5px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 3px;
  background-color: #4CAF50;
  color: white;
  font-size: 14px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.footer-buttons button:hover {
  background-color: #45a049;
}
You can place this code at the bottom of your HTML file, just before the closing </body> tag. The footer will have a light gray background color and centered text. The buttons will have a green background color, white text, and a hover effect that darkens the background color.

Feel free to adjust the CSS properties, such as colors, padding, or font sizes, to match the style of your website.






